query: UPDATE patients SET nationality = 'Kuwaiti' WHERE LOWER(TRIM(nationality)) IN ('kuwaiti', 'kuwait', 'kuwaitt'); UPDATE patients SET nationality = 'Non-Kuwaiti' WHERE LOWER(TRIM(nationality)) IN ('non kuwaiti', 'non kuwait', 'non');
